descriptionMarkdown:
A little design I made while trying to figure out how to make a load balancer in early game on a new world.
1. Place down the blueprint and assemble the parts
2. Put the items you want in the chest (leading to a main bus, boilers, etc.) or have them filtered in from another chest or miner
3. Profit! You now have a load balancer without the use of splitters and the like. Enjoy!

(Personally I use this for my coal line, so the burner inserters can self fuel. You can replace the burners with electrical powered inserters if you like, for other things)
title: Early Game Belt Balancer
